  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EWe understand that you may need to take time off for various personal or family reasons beyond standard vacation or sick leave. This General Leave of Absence Policy provides an overview of the different types of unpaid leaves that may be available to you, such as personal leaves, and outlines the general eligibility requirements and application procedures. We aim to support you during times when extended leave is necessary, ensuring a clear process for requesting and managing such absences.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
